      "id": "PopularPost335973",
      "post_content": "This card is under rated... . It's a counterspell for 2 cmc.. Plus it recasts their own spell for you.. This is under costed.. Should be 3cmc..  \n  \nCompare this to [twincast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=twincast)... If your opponent is casting a damage or removal spell, which of these would you rather be holding? No idea how people rate cards on here or why....  \n  \nRun 2 - 4 of these in most of my blue decks. Very blue card to the core.",
