    {
      "id": "PopularPost354491",
      "post_content": "\\*GRUMBLE GRUMBLE\\* All you young whippersnappers with your Redirects! Why when I was your age we paid 4 CMC and could only change the target of target spell with a SINGLE target, and we liked it! Every now and then we might have been able to discard a blue card from our hand from the game as alternate cost to do the same thing with a different card, but only if we were really good. You kids don't know how good ya got it! \\*GRUMBLE GRUMBLE\\*",
      "posted_by": "R1p_v4n_54u3r",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost354491\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">*GRUMBLE GRUMBLE* All you young whippersnappers with your Redirects!  Why when I was your age we paid 4 CMC and could only change the target of target spell with a SINGLE target, and we liked it!  Every now and then we might have been able to discard a blue card from our hand from the game as alternate cost to do the same thing with a different card, but only if we were really good.  You kids don't know how good ya got it!  *GRUMBLE GRUMBLE*</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '354491'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy103945\">R1p_v4n_54u3r</span>\r\n                                (12/14/2013 12:22:32 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../.