    {
      "id": "PopularPost355918",
      "post_content": "This card seems amazing at first, and it is when it works. Once I started playing it, I realized that it has some serious limitations. It can't stop [Essence Scatter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Essence Scatter) under most circumstances, nor can it stop spells when there are no other legal targets, which happens a lot against artifact and enchantment removal spells, nor abilities like [Oblivion Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Ring).  \n  \nOn the plus side you can 2 for 1 your opponent, steal an aura, target their hexproof creature.  \n  \nIt can be very satisfying to use, and if you opponent complains, tell them they just got taste of their own medicine.",
      "posted_by": "yesennes",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost355918\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">This card seems amazing at first, and it is when it works. Once I started playing it, I realized that it has some serious limitations. It can't stop <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Essence Scatter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Essence Scatter\">Essence Scatter</a> under most circumstances, nor can it stop spells when there are no other legal targets, which happens a lot against artifact and enchantment removal spells, nor abilities like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Oblivion Ring\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Ring\">Oblivion Ring</a>.<br/><br/>On the plus side you can 2 for 1 your opponent, steal an aura, target their hexproof creature.<br/><br/>It can be very satisfying to use, and if you opponent complains, tell them they just got taste of their own medicine.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '355918'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy95930\">yesennes</span>\r\n                                (12/27/2013 3:18:49 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                        