    {
      "id": "PopularPost343880",
      "post_content": "Often a 2-for-1 when used on a removal spell, and can fight counterspell wars. Also can answer uncounterable removal spells like [Abrupt Decay](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Abrupt Decay) and [Combust](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Combust). As a bonus, it even gets around hexproof when used on an opponent's removal spell. Highly underrated card.",
      "posted_by": "absreim",
